ible Praktiken des Tauschens und Teilens sichern so - auch über das Wasser hinaus - den Zugang zu knappen Ressourcen wie Land oder Nahrung.  aInstitutional Blueprints and Local Cooperation: The Rural Water Supply in Namibia.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aRural developmentzNamibia. 4aAfrika. 4aCommunity-Based Management. 4aEthnologie. 4aHumanökologie. 4aKommunale Wirtschaft. 4aKooperation. 4aKultur. 4aNamibia. 4aNatur. 4aNatürliche Ressourcen. 4aPastoralismus. 4aSoziale Netzwerke. 4aTauschökonomie. 4aUmweltsoziologie. 4aWasser. 4aWasserversorgung. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh  aAfrica.  aBarter Economy.  aCommunity-Based Management.  aCooperation.  aCulture.  aEnvironmental Sociology.  aEthnology.  aHuman Ecology.  aMunicipal Economy.  aNamibia.  aNatural Resources.  aNature.  aPastoralism.  aSocial Networks.  aWater Supply.  aWater.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2017z9783110548242oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839440483zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839440483423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839440483/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSWb2017